text: Aquilino Martin de la Llana Pimentel III, commonly known as Koko Pimentel, (born January 20, 1964) is a Filipino politician. He was the 28th Senate President of the Philippines from 2016 through 2018.Lardizabal. C. (2016, July 26). Koko Pimentel elected as Senate President of 17th Congress .
